  m_text: "Welcome, Survivor.\r\n\r\nThe world is your enemy, and every breath is
    earned.\n\r\n<color=#FF0000><u>Your Health Bar drains with every action - Walking,
    Running, and Jumping each take their toll at different rates.</u></color> \r\n\r\nThere
    are no tools here, only your instincts. Find food to stay alive and unlock powerful
    abilities through your Skill Tree. Choose your path wisely to navigate the wilds
    and overcome the dangers ahead.\r\nEvolve to survive. Move smart, or perish."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
